flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|strength_1|1|Finding a fresh way in|You can often see a different route into the work when the obvious one feels flat. This helps you unlock progress without forcing it through a standard path.|creative_movement|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::strength_1
flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|strength_2|2|Giving ideas enough weight|You are likely to do your best creative work when the strongest idea gets focused attention. This helps the idea become more than an interesting possibility.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::strength_2
flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|strength_3|3|Clearing crowded thinking|When too many ideas are active, movement or a change of pace can help you see what matters next. This gives the pattern a practical way to reduce noise.|physical_rhythm|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::strength_3
