13_Application
domain_key|pattern_key|application_area|guidance_type|priority|guidance_text|linked_signal_key|status|lookup_key
flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|use_this_when|guidance|1|Use this pattern when the work needs a fresh angle, a rough first version, or a way past a fixed approach. Let ideas move first, then choose the direction with the most promise.|creative_movement|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::use_this_when
flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|watch_for|guidance|2|Watch for the moment when exploring more options stops improving the work. That is often the point to focus, decide, or ask one useful person what is landing clearly.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::watch_for
flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|develop_by|guidance|3|Develop by choosing one promising idea earlier than feels natural. Give it focused time, then test it with someone before opening another round of possibilities.|social_exchange|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::develop_by
14_Closing_Integration
domain_key|pattern_key|score_shape|closing_summary|core_gift|core_trap|development_edge|memorable_line|status|lookup_key
flow_state|creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|concentrated|This result points to a flow style built around movement, then substance. You are likely to do your best work when ideas can open first, then the strongest direction gets enough focus, movement, and outside testing to become useful.|Your gift is the ability to generate original possibilities and turn the best ones into work with substance.|The trap is keeping too many angles open after the work needs a clearer choice.|The useful edge is to choose the strongest idea sooner and test it before expanding it again.|Let the idea move. Then choose the one that can carry the work.|active|flow_state::creative_movement_deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::concentrated
